<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
zap [wand] [target] : zap someone with a wand<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
You use the zap command to use one of your wands upon a target.  Wands<br>
generally have charges and the use of zap will expend a charge.  When<br>
depleted of all of their charges, wands make excellent kindling.  You must<br>
be holding a wand in order to be able to zap with it.<br>
</html>
</body>
